<reference id="reference_ntt_lkg_pvb">
    <title>Proxy Settings</title>
    <refbody>
        <section id="section_q2x_4kg_pvb">
            <p><ph conkeyref="PRODvars/PRODUCT_SP_ALTERNATIVE_NAME">OFFICIAL_PRODUCT_NAME</ph> use a
                proxy for both communication with <ph
                    conkeyref="PRODvars/PRODUCT_SERVER_ALTERNATIVE_NAME"/> and scan component
                updates.</p>
            <p>It is configurable using <ph conkeyref="PRODvars/SETUP_FILE"/> before installation
                and the command line interface afterwards.</p>
            <ul id="ul_ynb_1n2_tvb">
                <li>
                    <p>For more information about using <ph conkeyref="PRODvars/SETUP_FILE"/> to
                        configure the proxy settings before installation, refer to <xref
                            href="silent_install_configuration=20221122140149.xml"/>.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>For more information about using command line interface to configure the
                        proxy settings after installation, refer to <xref
                            href="cli_list_sp=20221208151252.xml"/></p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>
